From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
Date: Mon, 27 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] hwmon: gxp-power: add missing MODULE_LICENSE

The gxp-power module is missing the MODULE_LICENSE macro, causing
build failures with modpost error:

  FATAL: modpost: missing MODULE_LICENSE() in drivers/hwmon/gxp-power.o

Add MODULE_LICENSE("GPL") to fix the build.

Signed-off-by: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
---
 drivers/hwmon/gxp-power.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/hwmon/gxp-power.c b/drivers/hwmon/gxp-power.c
--- a/drivers/hwmon/gxp-power.c
+++ b/drivers/hwmon/gxp-power.c
@@ -118,3 +118,4 @@ module_platform_driver(gxp_power_driver);

 MODULE_AUTHOR("Louis Hsu <kai-hsiang.hsu@hpe.com>");
 MODULE_DESCRIPTION("HPE GXP POWER driver");
+MODULE_LICENSE("GPL");
